## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all perspectives on the issue. The complexity of human cognition and the rapidly changing media landscape mean that new factors influencing the belief in fake news may emerge. Additionally, cultural and regional differences in media consumption and trust were not extensively covered in this report.